                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17860222-15-defend255 t17860222-15-punish94"></join>
               Transported for seven years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury before Mr. Justice GOULD.</p>
